msgid "CRM module for managing leads, contacts, and opportunities."
msgstr ""
"Module CRM pour la gestion des prospects, des contacts et des opportunites."

msgid ""
"Refactored leads core views into tab sub-packages and opportunities split "
"and stages views into sub-packages. Standardized first-party import section "
"headers and migrated transaction imports to horilla.db. Leads: fixed Go to "
"Leads navigation from convert success modal; enhanced web-to-lead form with "
"Select2 and improved styling. Opportunities: fixed team selling and split "
"checks via _resolve_company and all_objects OpportunitySettings lookups; "
"scoped OpportunityTeamForm user choices to active company."
msgstr ""
"Refactorisation des vues principales des leads en sous-paquets a onglets et "
"des vues de split et d'etapes des opportunites en sous-paquets. "
"Standardisation des en-tetes de section d'import internes et migration des "
"imports de transactions vers horilla.db. Leads : correction de la navigation"
" vers les leads depuis la modale de succes de conversion ; amelioration du "
"formulaire web-to-lead avec Select2 et du style. Opportunites : correction "
"de la vente en equipe et des verifications de split via _resolve_company et "
"les recherches all_objects OpportunitySettings ; restriction des choix "
"utilisateur d'OpportunityTeamForm a la societe active."

msgid ""
"Lead and opportunity stage saving now validates first and uses update-or-"
"create instead of delete-and-recreate, so stages still referenced by leads "
"or opportunities are no longer deleted (preventing ProtectedError on the "
"PROTECT FKs). CSRF protection restored on stage-group and custom-stage views"
" with csrf_token added to the HTMX forms. Fixed KeyError on multi-step "
"create forms by removing direct created_by / updated_by access stripped by "
"HorillaMultiStepForm. Removed redundant fields attributes superseded by "
"form_class on forecast, assignment-rule, opportunity-team, and scoring-rule "
"single-form views, plus docstring coverage for pylint compliance."
msgstr ""
"La sauvegarde des etapes de lead et d'opportunite effectue desormais une "
"validation prealable et utilise update-or-create au lieu de delete-and-"
"recreate, de sorte que les etapes encore referencees par des leads ou des "
"opportunites ne sont plus supprimees (evitant ProtectedError sur les PROTECT"
" FKs). Protection CSRF restauree sur les vues stage-group et custom-stage "
"avec csrf_token ajoute aux formulaires HTMX. Correction de KeyError dans les"
" formulaires de creation multi-etapes en supprimant l'acces direct a "
"created_by/updated_by retire par HorillaMultiStepForm. Suppression des "
"attributs fields redondants remplaces par form_class sur les vues de "
"formulaire unique, avec couverture docstring pour la conformite pylint."

msgid ""
"Aligned with platform 1.10: imports and integrations target contrib packages"
" and short Django app labels (core, generics, mail, activity, and other "
"shared modules). URL namespaces, static paths, permission strings, and "
"ForeignKey string references updated where they cross into contrib apps; the"
" CRM module keeps its original app label and database table prefix."
msgstr ""
"Aligne sur la plateforme 1.10 : les imports et integrations ciblent les "
"paquets contrib et les labels d'application Django courts (core, generics, "
"mail, activity et autres modules partages). Espaces de noms URL, chemins "
"statiques, chaines de permissions et references de chaines ForeignKey mis a "
"jour la ou ils croisent les contrib apps ; le module CRM conserve son label "
"d'application d'origine et son prefixe de table de base de donnees."

msgid ""
"Enhanced CRM fixtures with additional fields. Improved UI refinements "
"including navbar z-index fixes, KPI color consistency, and standardized "
"template formatting across leads, accounts, campaigns, contacts, and "
"opportunities modules."
msgstr ""
"Enrichissement des fixtures CRM avec des champs supplementaires. "
"Ameliorations de l'interface utilisateur incluant des corrections de z-index"
" de la barre de navigation, la coherence des couleurs KPI et la "
"standardisation du formatage des templates dans les modules leads, accounts,"
" campaigns, contacts et opportunities."

msgid ""
"Introduced advanced CRM visualization capabilities including chart views, "
"timeline (Gantt-style) views, split layout navigation, and card-based record"
" views. Improved pipeline data exploration and navigation across Leads, "
"Accounts, Campaigns, Contacts, and Opportunities."
msgstr ""
"Introduction de fonctionnalites de visualisation CRM avancees incluant des "
"vues graphiques, des vues chronologiques (style Gantt), une navigation en "
"disposition fractionnee et des vues d'enregistrements en cartes. "
"Amelioration de l'exploration des donnees pipeline et de la navigation dans "
"Leads, Accounts, Campaigns, Contacts et Opportunities."

msgid ""
"Enabled advanced quick filters, improved column selector behavior, refined "
"CRM list view consistency, and enhanced filtering reliability across Leads, "
"Accounts, Contacts, Campaigns, and Opportunities."
msgstr ""
"Activation des filtres rapides avances, amelioration du comportement du "
"selecteur de colonnes, affinement de la coherence de la vue liste CRM et "
"fiabilite accrue du filtrage dans Leads, Accounts, Contacts, Campaigns et "
"Opportunities."

msgid ""
"Migrated CRM sub-apps to Horilla AppLauncher and replaced Django utilities "
"with horilla.utils.decorators, horilla.utils.translation, and "
"horilla.shortcuts where applicable."
msgstr ""
"Migration des sous-applications CRM vers Horilla AppLauncher et remplacement"
" des utilitaires Django par horilla.utils.decorators, "
"horilla.utils.translation et horilla.shortcuts le cas echeant."
